OL,3,CDuck & Dry to open new sites after
OL,4,Cstriking Hero Brands partnership deal
OL,6,FRestaurant backer Hero Brands is to
OL,7,Fexpand into beauty for the first time
OL,8,Fafter striking a deal with blow-dry
OL,9,Fchain Duck & Dry.
OL,11,FThe partnership deal between the
OL,12,Fbrands will help drive an ambitious
OL,13,Fexpansion programme for Duck & Dry,
OL,14,Fwith plans for 10 new UK stores this
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FIn recent weeks, the brand has opened
OL,18,Fsites in Notting Hill's The Whiteley
OL,19,Fdevelopment and John Lewis Oxford
OL,20,FStreet.
