OL,3,CDuck & Dry to open new sites after
OL,4,Cstriking Hero Brands partnership deal
OL,6,FIt will soon be opening a new location
OL,7,Fin Battersea Power Station as it
OL,8,Fcontinues to grow across the capital.
OL,10,FIt represents a new sector for Hero
OL,11,FBrands, which operates more than 190
OL,12,Flocations globally.
OL,14,FHero Brands operates across media,
OL,15,Flicensing, lifestyle and food and
OL,16,Fbeverage brands ` including German
OL,17,FDoner Kebab and Sidemen-backed chain
OL,18,FSides.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
