OL,3,CDuck & Dry to open new sites after
OL,4,Cstriking Hero Brands partnership deal
OL,6,FAthif Sarwar, chairman at Hero Brands,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Beauty is a category we've long
OL,8,Fseen potential in, and Duck & Dry is
OL,9,Fthe perfect partner for Hero Brands'
OL,10,Fentry into the space.
OL,12,F"Their creativity and cultural pull
OL,13,Falign with our ambition to build the
OL,14,Fnext generation of consumer brands.
OL,16,F"This move unlocks major potential to
OL,17,Ftake Duck & Dry from a salon brand to
OL,18,Fa full consumer lifestyle experience."
