OL,3,CDuck & Dry to open new sites after
OL,4,Cstriking Hero Brands partnership deal
OL,6,FYulia Rorstrom, chief executive and
OL,7,Ffounder at Duck & Dry, said the deal
OL,8,Fwill help provide scale and support to
OL,9,Fdrive its growth ambitions.
OL,11,FShe said: "This is a huge moment for
OL,12,Fus.
OL,14,F"Moving from founderled to
OL,15,Fpartnershippowered gives Duck & Dry
OL,16,Fthe strength and scale to grow without
OL,17,Flosing the creativity and confidence
OL,18,Fthat make us who we are.
